      "text": "Tâ darrija wiꞥſch ar wiſ-\nfeemi Galdeem ta Dsihwokta /\nwisch darrija arridsan ta Dsih-\nwokta Galdus/ diwidefinits Gal-\ndus / Deenas-Widdus puffê.\n"
